        "content": "<p>Hi, </p>\n<p>I wanted to update my installation of Lean from 4.0 to 4.1.</p>\n<p>On windows I opened an admin terminal and ran <code>elan update</code></p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code> <span class=\"n\">leanprover</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">lean4</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"n\">nightly</span> <span class=\"n\">update</span> <span class=\"n\">failed</span> <span class=\"bp\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">Lean</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">version</span> <span class=\"mi\">4</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"n\">nightly</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">2022</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">06</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">09</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">commit</span> <span class=\"n\">d0499ebf4d92</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Release</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">error</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">could</span> <span class=\"n\">not</span> <span class=\"n\">remove</span> <span class=\"bp\">'</span><span class=\"n\">elan</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"n\">bin'</span> <span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"bp\">'</span><span class=\"n\">C</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"bp\">\\</span><span class=\"n\">Users</span><span class=\"bp\">\\</span><span class=\"n\">myUserName</span><span class=\"bp\">\\.</span><span class=\"n\">elan</span><span class=\"bp\">\\</span><span class=\"n\">bin</span><span class=\"bp\">\\</span><span class=\"n\">elan.exe'</span>\n<span class=\"n\">info</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">caused</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Access</span> <span class=\"n\">is</span> <span class=\"n\">denied.</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">os</span> <span class=\"n\">error</span> <span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Is there another way to update the Lean version on Windows?</p>",
